  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bcb\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf 4 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "4 people were arrested for digging for gold in Madtu Arayampadi",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kaluvanchikudi Special Task Force has arrested and handed over 4 people who were involved in digging for gold in an abandoned land in Arayampathi Ollikkulam area of \u200b\u200bKathankudi Police Division, Batticaloa yesterday Tuesday (19) and handed them over.",
        "According to the information received by the Military Intelligence Unit, the Military Intelligence Unit along with Kalavanchikudi Special Task Force surrounded and laid siege to an abandoned land near the Garment Factory Hostel in the said area at 11.30 midnight yesterday.",
        "During this, two people from Ampara region who were engaged in digging for gold in the land, arrested 4 people including two from Arayampadi region and recovered the tools used for digging the land, shovel, shovel and call phone and handed them over to the police.",
        "The police said that steps have been taken to produce the arrested women in the court after investigation."
      ],
